name: Ripster
tweet: #tradingtips #optiontips  If you want to trade same week expiry, if you are new to options only trade those on Monday/Tuesday. The decay in options is fast and quick closer to friday. You can play Lottos(risk all) on thursday/friday if you can afford to do so but look for +100%

name: Ripster
tweet: #tradingtips #lottos Friday lottos close to expiry(same day far out of money) go to zero quickly, so only trade what u can lose all.  Gamma/Delta spikes up fast on these options but Theta and value will vanish up quickly if price does not move  Look for 100-200% gains on lotto

name: Ripster
tweet: #tradingtips #optiontips If you are taking options before breakout or before resistance break, take Longer term options to avoid decay/theta/sideways chop on your options. When in breakout u can take shorter term calls -1week as gamma/delta increase will give you quicker returns
